var book = {
	"name": "Revelation",
	"numChapters": 22,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>The revelation of Jesus Christ, which God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30683A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30683A\"></sup>gave him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30683B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30683B\"></sup>to show to his servants the things that must soon take place. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30683C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30683C\"></sup>He made it known by sending his angel to his servant John,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30684D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30684D\"></sup>who bore witness to the word of God and to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30684E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30684E\"></sup>the testimony of Jesus Christ, even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30684F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30684F\"></sup>to all that he saw.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30685G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30685G\"></sup>Blessed is the one who reads aloud the words of this prophecy, and blessed are those who hear, and who keep what is written in it, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30685H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30685H\"></sup>for the time is near.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>John to the seven churches that are in Asia:Grace to you and peace from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30686I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30686I\"></sup>him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30686J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30686J\"></sup>who is and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30686K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30686K\"></sup>who was and who is to come, and from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30686L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30686L\"></sup>the seven spirits who are before his throne,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>and from Jesus Christ <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30687M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30687M\"></sup>the faithful witness, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30687N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30687N\"></sup>the firstborn of the dead, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30687O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30687O\"></sup>the ruler of kings on earth.To <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30687P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30687P\"></sup>him who loves us and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30687Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30687Q\"></sup>has freed us from our sins by his blood",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>and made us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30688R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30688R\"></sup>a kingdom, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30688S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30688S\"></sup>priests to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30688T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30688T\"></sup>his God and Father, to him be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30688U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30688U\"></sup>glory and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30688V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30688V\"></sup>dominion forever and ever. Amen.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30689W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30689W\"></sup>he is coming with the clouds, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30689X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30689X\"></sup>every eye will see him, even those who pierced him, and all tribes of the earth will wail on account of him. Even so. Amen.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30690Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30690Y\"></sup>“I am the Alpha and the Omega,” says the Lord God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30690Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30690Z\"></sup>“who is and who was and who is to come, the Almighty.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>I, John, your brother and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30691AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30691AA\"></sup>partner in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30691AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30691AB\"></sup>the tribulation and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30691AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30691AC\"></sup>the kingdom and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30691AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30691AD\"></sup>the patient endurance that are in Jesus, was on the island called Patmos <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30691AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30691AE\"></sup>on account of the word of God and the testimony of Jesus.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30692AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30692AF\"></sup>I was in the Spirit <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30692AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30692AG\"></sup>on the Lord's day, and I heard behind me a loud voice <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30692AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30692AH\"></sup>like a trumpet",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>saying, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30693AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30693AI\"></sup>“Write what you see in a book and send it to the seven churches, to Ephesus and to Smyrna and to Pergamum and to Thyatira and to Sardis and to Philadelphia and to Laodicea.”</span>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then I turned to see the voice that was speaking to me, and on turning I saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30694AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30694AJ\"></sup>seven golden lampstands,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>and in the midst of the lampstands <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30695AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30695AK\"></sup>one like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30695AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30695AL\"></sup>a son of man, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30695AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30695AM\"></sup>clothed with a long robe and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30695AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30695AN\"></sup>with a golden sash around his chest.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30696AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30696AO\"></sup>The hairs of his head were white, like white wool, like snow. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30696AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30696AP\"></sup>His eyes were like a flame of fire,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30697AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30697AQ\"></sup>his feet were like burnished bronze, refined in a furnace, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30697AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30697AR\"></sup>his voice was like the roar of many waters.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30698AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30698AS\"></sup>In his right hand he held seven stars, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30698AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30698AT\"></sup>from his mouth came a sharp two-edged sword, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30698AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30698AU\"></sup>his face was like the sun shining <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30698AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30698AV\"></sup>in full strength.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30699AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30699AW\"></sup>When I saw him, I fell at his feet as though dead. But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30699AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30699AX\"></sup>he laid his right hand on me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30699AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30699AY\"></sup>saying, <span class=\"woj\">“Fear not, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30699AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30699AZ\"></sup>I am the first and the last,</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>and the living one. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30700BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30700BA\"></sup>I died, and behold I am alive forevermore, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30700BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30700BB\"></sup>I have the keys of Death and Hades.</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30701BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30701BC\"></sup>Write therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30701BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30701BD\"></sup>the things that you have seen, those that are and those that are to take place after this.</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>As for the mystery of the seven stars that you saw in my right hand, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30702BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30702BE\"></sup>the seven golden lampstands, the seven stars are the angels of the seven churches, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30702BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30702BF\"></sup>the seven lampstands are the seven churches.</span>"
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"woj\"><span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>“To the angel of the church in Ephesus write: ‘The words of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30703A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30703A\"></sup>him who holds the seven stars in his right hand, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30703B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30703B\"></sup>who walks among the seven golden lampstands.</span>",
			"2": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30704C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30704C\"></sup>“‘I know your works, your toil and your patient endurance, and how you cannot bear with those who are evil, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30704D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30704D\"></sup>have tested those <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30704E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30704E\"></sup>who call themselves apostles and are not, and found them to be false.</span>",
			"3": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>I know you are enduring patiently and bearing up <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30705F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30705F\"></sup>for my name's sake, and you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30705G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30705G\"></sup>have not grown weary.</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But I have this against you, that you have abandoned <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30706H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30706H\"></sup>the love you had at first.</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Remember therefore from where you have fallen; repent, and do <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30707I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30707I\"></sup>the works you did at first. If not, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30707J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30707J\"></sup>I will come to you and remove your lampstand from its place, unless you repent.</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Yet this you have: you hate the works of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30708K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30708K\"></sup>the Nicolaitans, which I also hate.</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30709L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30709L\"></sup>He who has an ear, let him hear what the Spirit says to the churches. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30709M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30709M\"></sup>To the one who conquers I will grant to eat of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30709N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30709N\"></sup>the tree of life, which is in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30709O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30709O\"></sup>the paradise of God.’</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“And to the angel of the church in Smyrna write: ‘The words of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30710P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30710P\"></sup>the first and the last, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30710Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30710Q\"></sup>who died and came to life.</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“‘I know your tribulation and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30711R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30711R\"></sup>your poverty (<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30711S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30711S\"></sup>but you are rich) and the slander of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30711T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30711T\"></sup>those who say that they are Jews and are not, but are a synagogue of Satan.</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Do not fear what you are about to suffer. Behold, the devil is about to throw some of you into prison, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30712U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30712U\"></sup>that you may be tested, and for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30712V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30712V\"></sup>ten days <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30712W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30712W\"></sup>you will have tribulation. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30712X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30712X\"></sup>Be faithful <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30712Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30712Y\"></sup>unto death, and I will give you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30712Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30712Z\"></sup>the crown of life.</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30713AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30713AA\"></sup>He who has an ear, let him hear what the Spirit says to the churches. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30713AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30713AB\"></sup>The one who conquers will not be hurt by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30713AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30713AC\"></sup>the second death.’</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“And to the angel of the church in Pergamum write: ‘The words of him who has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30714AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30714AD\"></sup>the sharp two-edged sword.</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“‘I know where you dwell, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30715AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30715AE\"></sup>where Satan's throne is. Yet you hold fast my name, and you did not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30715AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30715AF\"></sup>deny my faith even in the days of Antipas <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30715AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30715AG\"></sup>my faithful witness, who was killed among you, where Satan dwells.</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But I have a few things against you: you have some there who hold the teaching of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30716AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30716AH\"></sup>Balaam, who taught Balak to put a stumbling block before the sons of Israel, so that they might <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30716AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30716AI\"></sup>eat food sacrificed to idols and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30716AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30716AJ\"></sup>practice sexual immorality.</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>So also you have some who hold the teaching of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30717AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30717AK\"></sup>the Nicolaitans.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Therefore repent. If not, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30718AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30718AL\"></sup>I will come to you soon and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30718AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30718AM\"></sup>war against them with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30718AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30718AN\"></sup>the sword of my mouth.</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30719AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30719AO\"></sup>He who has an ear, let him hear what the Spirit says to the churches. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30719AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30719AP\"></sup>To the one who conquers I will give some of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30719AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30719AQ\"></sup>the hidden manna, and I will give him a white stone, with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30719AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30719AR\"></sup>a new name written on the stone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30719AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30719AS\"></sup>that no one knows except the one who receives it.’</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“And to the angel of the church in Thyatira write: ‘The words of the Son of God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30720AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30720AT\"></sup>who has eyes like a flame of fire, and whose feet are like burnished bronze.</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30721AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30721AU\"></sup>“‘I know your works, your love and faith and service and patient endurance, and that your latter works exceed the first.</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>But I have this against you, that you tolerate that woman <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30722AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30722AV\"></sup>Jezebel, who calls herself a prophetess and is teaching and seducing my servants <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30722AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30722AW\"></sup>to practice sexual immorality and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30722AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30722AX\"></sup>to eat food sacrificed to idols.</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>I gave her time to repent, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30723AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30723AY\"></sup>she refuses to repent of her sexual immorality.</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Behold, I will throw her onto a sickbed, and those who commit adultery with her I will throw into great tribulation, unless they repent of her works,</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>and I will strike her children dead. And all the churches will know that I am he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30725AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30725AZ\"></sup>who searches mind and heart, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30725BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30725BA\"></sup>I will give to each of you according to your works.</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>But to the rest of you in Thyatira, who do not hold this teaching, who have not learned what some call <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30726BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30726BB\"></sup>the deep things of Satan, to you I say, I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30726BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30726BC\"></sup>do not lay on you any other burden.</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Only hold fast <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30727BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30727BD\"></sup>what you have until I come.</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30728BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30728BE\"></sup>The one who conquers and who keeps my works <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30728BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30728BF\"></sup>until the end, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30728BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30728BG\"></sup>to him I will give authority over the nations,</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30729BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30729BH\"></sup>he will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30729BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30729BI\"></sup>rule them with a rod of iron, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30729BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30729BJ\"></sup>as when earthen pots are broken in pieces, even as I myself have received authority from my Father.</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>And I will give him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30730BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30730BK\"></sup>the morning star.</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30731BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30731BL\"></sup>He who has an ear, let him hear what the Spirit says to the churches.’</span>"
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"woj\"><span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>“And to the angel of the church in Sardis write: ‘The words of him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30732A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30732A\"></sup>who has the seven spirits of God and the seven stars.</span><span class=\"woj\">“‘I know your works. You have the reputation <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30732B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30732B\"></sup>of being alive, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30732C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30732C\"></sup>but you are dead.</span>",
			"2": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Wake up, and strengthen what remains and is about to die, for I have not found your works <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30733D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30733D\"></sup>complete in the sight of my God.</span>",
			"3": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30734E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30734E\"></sup>Remember, then, what you received and heard. Keep it, and repent. If you will not wake up, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30734F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30734F\"></sup>I will come <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30734G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30734G\"></sup>like a thief, and you will not know at what hour I will come against you.</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Yet you have still a few names in Sardis, people who have not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30735H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30735H\"></sup>soiled their garments, and they will walk with me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30735I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30735I\"></sup>in white, for they are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30735J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30735J\"></sup>worthy.</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30736K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30736K\"></sup>The one who conquers will be clothed thus in white garments, and I will never <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30736L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30736L\"></sup>blot his name out of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30736M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30736M\"></sup>the book of life. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30736N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30736N\"></sup>I will confess his name before my Father and before his angels.</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30737O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30737O\"></sup>He who has an ear, let him hear what the Spirit says to the churches.’</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“And to the angel of the church in Philadelphia write: ‘The words of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30738P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30738P\"></sup>the holy one, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30738Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30738Q\"></sup>the true one, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30738R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30738R\"></sup>who has the key of David, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30738S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30738S\"></sup>who opens and no one will shut, who shuts and no one opens.</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“‘I know your works. Behold, I have set before you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30739T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30739T\"></sup>an open door, which no one is able to shut. I know that you have but little power, and yet you have kept my word and have not denied my name.</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Behold, I will make those of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30740U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30740U\"></sup>the synagogue of Satan who say that they are Jews and are not, but lie—behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30740V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30740V\"></sup>I will make them come and bow down before your feet, and they will learn that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30740W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30740W\"></sup>I have loved you.</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30741X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30741X\"></sup>Because you have kept my word about patient endurance, I will keep you from the hour of trial that is coming on the whole world, to try <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30741Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30741Y\"></sup>those who dwell on the earth.</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30742Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30742Z\"></sup>I am coming soon. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30742AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30742AA\"></sup>Hold fast what you have, so that no one may seize <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30742AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30742AB\"></sup>your crown.</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30743AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30743AC\"></sup>The one who conquers, I will make him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30743AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30743AD\"></sup>a pillar in the temple of my God. Never shall he go out of it, and I will write on him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30743AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30743AE\"></sup>the name of my God, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30743AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30743AF\"></sup>the name of the city of my God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30743AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30743AG\"></sup>the new Jerusalem, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30743AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30743AH\"></sup>which comes down from my God out of heaven, and my own <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30743AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30743AI\"></sup>new name.</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30744AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30744AJ\"></sup>He who has an ear, let him hear what the Spirit says to the churches.’</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“And to the angel of the church in Laodicea write: ‘The words of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30745AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30745AK\"></sup>Amen, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30745AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30745AL\"></sup>the faithful and true witness, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30745AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30745AM\"></sup>the beginning of God's creation.</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“‘I know your works: you are neither cold nor hot. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30746AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30746AN\"></sup>Would that you were either cold or hot!</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>So, because you are lukewarm, and neither hot nor cold, I will spit you out of my mouth.</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30748AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30748AO\"></sup>For you say, I am rich, I have prospered, and I need nothing, not realizing that you are wretched, pitiable, poor, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30748AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30748AP\"></sup>blind, and naked.</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>I counsel you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30749AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30749AQ\"></sup>to buy from me gold refined by fire, so that you may be rich, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30749AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30749AR\"></sup>white garments so that you may clothe yourself and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30749AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30749AS\"></sup>the shame of your nakedness may not be seen, and salve to anoint your eyes, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30749AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30749AT\"></sup>so that you may see.</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30750AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30750AU\"></sup>Those whom I love, I reprove and discipline, so be zealous and repent.</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Behold, I stand at the door and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30751AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30751AV\"></sup>knock. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30751AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30751AW\"></sup>If anyone hears my voice and opens the door, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30751AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30751AX\"></sup>I will come in to him and eat with him, and he with me.</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30752AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30752AY\"></sup>The one who conquers, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30752AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30752AZ\"></sup>I will grant him to sit with me on my throne, as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30752BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30752BA\"></sup>I also conquered and sat down with my Father on his throne.</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30753BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30753BB\"></sup>He who has an ear, let him hear what the Spirit says to the churches.’”</span>"
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>After this I looked, and behold, a door standing open in heaven! And the first voice, which I had heard speaking to me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30754A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30754A\"></sup>like a trumpet, said, <span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30754B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30754B\"></sup>“Come up here, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30754C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30754C\"></sup>I will show you what must take place after this.”</span>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>At once <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30755D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30755D\"></sup>I was in the Spirit, and behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30755E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30755E\"></sup>a throne stood in heaven, with one seated on the throne.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And he who sat there had the appearance of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30756F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30756F\"></sup>jasper and carnelian, and around the throne was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30756G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30756G\"></sup>a rainbow that had the appearance of an emerald.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Around the throne were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30757H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30757H\"></sup>twenty-four thrones, and seated on the thrones were twenty-four elders, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30757I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30757I\"></sup>clothed in white garments, with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30757J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30757J\"></sup>golden crowns on their heads.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>From the throne came <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30758K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30758K\"></sup>flashes of lightning, and rumblings and peals of thunder, and before the throne were burning <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30758L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30758L\"></sup>seven torches of fire, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30758M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30758M\"></sup>which are the seven spirits of God,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>and before the throne there was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30759N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30759N\"></sup>as it were a sea of glass, like crystal.And around the throne, on each side of the throne, are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30759O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30759O\"></sup>four living creatures, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30759P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30759P\"></sup>full of eyes in front and behind:",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30760Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30760Q\"></sup>the first living creature like a lion, the second living creature like an ox, the third living creature with the face of a man, and the fourth living creature like an eagle in flight.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And the four living creatures, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30761R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30761R\"></sup>each of them with six wings, are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30761S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30761S\"></sup>full of eyes all around and within, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30761T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30761T\"></sup>day and night they never cease to say,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30761U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30761U\"></sup>“Holy, holy, holy, is the Lord God Almighty,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30761V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30761V\"></sup>who was and is and is to come!”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And whenever the living creatures give glory and honor and thanks to him who is seated on the throne, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30762W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30762W\"></sup>who lives forever and ever,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>the twenty-four elders <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30763X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30763X\"></sup>fall down before him who is seated on the throne and worship him who lives forever and ever. They cast <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30763Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30763Y\"></sup>their crowns before the throne, saying,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30764Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30764Z\"></sup>“Worthy are you, our Lord and God,to receive glory and honor and power,for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30764AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30764AA\"></sup>you created all things,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30764AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30764AB\"></sup>by your will they existed and were created.”"
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span>Then I saw in the right hand of him who was seated on the throne <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30765A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30765A\"></sup>a scroll written within and on the back, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30765B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30765B\"></sup>sealed with seven seals.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30766C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30766C\"></sup>I saw a mighty angel proclaiming with a loud voice, “Who is worthy to open the scroll and break its seals?”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And no one in heaven or on earth or under the earth was able to open the scroll or to look into it,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>and I began to weep loudly because no one was found worthy to open the scroll or to look into it.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And one of the elders said to me, “Weep no more; behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30769D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30769D\"></sup>the Lion <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30769E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30769E\"></sup>of the tribe of Judah, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30769F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30769F\"></sup>the Root of David, has conquered, so that he can open the scroll and its seven seals.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And between the throne and the four living creatures and among the elders I saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30770G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30770G\"></sup>a Lamb standing, as though it had been slain, with seven horns and with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30770H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30770H\"></sup>seven eyes, which are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30770I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30770I\"></sup>the seven spirits of God sent out into all the earth.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And he went and took the scroll from the right hand of him who was seated on the throne.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And when he had taken the scroll, the four living creatures and the twenty-four elders <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30772J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30772J\"></sup>fell down before the Lamb, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30772K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30772K\"></sup>each holding a harp, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30772L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30772L\"></sup>golden bowls full of incense, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30772M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30772M\"></sup>which are the prayers of the saints.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And they sang <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30773N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30773N\"></sup>a new song, saying,“Worthy are you to take the scrolland to open its seals,for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30773O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30773O\"></sup>you were slain, and by your blood <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30773P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30773P\"></sup>you ransomed people for Godfrom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30773Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30773Q\"></sup>every tribe and language and people and nation,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>and you have made them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30774R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30774R\"></sup>a kingdom and priests to our God,and they shall reign on the earth.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then I looked, and I heard around the throne and the living creatures and the elders the voice of many angels, numbering <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30775S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30775S\"></sup>myriads of myriads and thousands of thousands,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>saying with a loud voice, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30776T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30776T\"></sup>“Worthy is the Lamb who was slain,to receive power and wealth and wisdom and mightand honor and glory and blessing!”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And I heard <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30777U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30777U\"></sup>every creature in heaven and on earth and under the earth and in the sea, and all that is in them, saying, “To him who sits on the throne and to the Lambbe blessing and honor and glory and might forever and ever!”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And the four living creatures <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30778V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30778V\"></sup>said, “Amen!” and the elders <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30778W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30778W\"></sup>fell down and worshiped."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span>Now I watched when the Lamb opened one of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30779A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30779A\"></sup>the seven seals, and I heard <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30779B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30779B\"></sup>one of the four living creatures say <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30779C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30779C\"></sup>with a voice like thunder, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30779D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30779D\"></sup>“Come!”",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And I looked, and behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30780E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30780E\"></sup>a white horse! And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30780F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30780F\"></sup>its rider had a bow, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30780G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30780G\"></sup>a crown was given to him, and he came out <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30780H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30780H\"></sup>conquering, and to conquer.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>When he opened the second seal, I heard <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30781I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30781I\"></sup>the second living creature say, “Come!”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And out came another horse, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30782J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30782J\"></sup>bright red. Its rider was permitted <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30782K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30782K\"></sup>to take peace from the earth, so that people should slay one another, and he was given a great sword.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>When he opened the third seal, I heard the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30783L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30783L\"></sup>third living creature say, “Come!” And I looked, and behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30783M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30783M\"></sup>a black horse! And its rider had a pair of scales in his hand.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And I heard what seemed to be a voice in the midst of the four living creatures, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30784N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30784N\"></sup>“A quart of wheat for a denarius, and three quarts of barley for a denarius, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30784O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30784O\"></sup>do not harm the oil and wine!”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>When he opened the fourth seal, I heard the voice of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30785P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30785P\"></sup>the fourth living creature say, “Come!”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And I looked, and behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30786Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30786Q\"></sup>a pale horse! And its rider's name was Death, and Hades followed him. And they were given authority over a fourth of the earth, to kill <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30786R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30786R\"></sup>with sword and with famine and with pestilence and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30786S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30786S\"></sup>by wild beasts of the earth.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>When he opened the fifth seal, I saw under <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30787T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30787T\"></sup>the altar <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30787U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30787U\"></sup>the souls of those who had been slain <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30787V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30787V\"></sup>for the word of God and for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30787W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30787W\"></sup>the witness they had borne.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>They cried out with a loud voice, “O Sovereign Lord, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30788X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30788X\"></sup>holy and true, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30788Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30788Y\"></sup>how long <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30788Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30788Z\"></sup>before you will judge and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30788AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30788AA\"></sup>avenge our blood on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30788AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30788AB\"></sup>those who dwell on the earth?”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then they were each given <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30789AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30789AC\"></sup>a white robe and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30789AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30789AD\"></sup>told to rest a little longer, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30789AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30789AE\"></sup>until the number of their fellow servants and their brothers <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30789AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30789AF\"></sup>should be complete, who were to be killed as they themselves had been.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>When he opened the sixth seal, I looked, and behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30790AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30790AG\"></sup>there was a great earthquake, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30790AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30790AH\"></sup>the sun became black as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30790AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30790AI\"></sup>sackcloth, the full moon became like blood,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30791AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30791AJ\"></sup>the stars of the sky fell to the earth <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30791AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30791AK\"></sup>as the fig tree sheds its winter fruit when shaken by a gale.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30792AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30792AL\"></sup>The sky vanished <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30792AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30792AM\"></sup>like a scroll that is being rolled up, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30792AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30792AN\"></sup>every mountain and island was removed from its place.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Then the kings of the earth and the great ones and the generals and the rich and the powerful, and everyone, slave and free, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30793AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30793AO\"></sup>hid themselves in the caves and among the rocks of the mountains,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30794AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30794AP\"></sup>calling to the mountains and rocks, “Fall on us and hide us from the face of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30794AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30794AQ\"></sup>him who is seated on the throne, and from the wrath of the Lamb,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30795AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30795AR\"></sup>the great day of their wrath has come, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30795AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30795AS\"></sup>who can stand?”"
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">7 </span>After this I saw four angels standing at the four corners of the earth, holding back <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30796A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30796A\"></sup>the four winds of the earth, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30796B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30796B\"></sup>that no wind might blow on earth or sea or against any tree.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Then I saw another angel ascending <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30797C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30797C\"></sup>from the rising of the sun, with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30797D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30797D\"></sup>the seal of the living God, and he called with a loud voice to the four angels who had been given power to harm earth and sea,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30798E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30798E\"></sup>“Do not harm the earth or the sea or the trees, until we have sealed the servants of our God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30798F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30798F\"></sup>on their foreheads.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30799G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30799G\"></sup>I heard the number of the sealed, 144,000, sealed from every tribe of the sons of Israel:",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>12,000 from the tribe of Judah were sealed,12,000 from the tribe of Reuben,12,000 from the tribe of Gad,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>12,000 from the tribe of Asher,12,000 from the tribe of Naphtali,12,000 from the tribe of Manasseh,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>12,000 from the tribe of Simeon,12,000 from the tribe of Levi,12,000 from the tribe of Issachar,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>12,000 from the tribe of Zebulun,12,000 from the tribe of Joseph,12,000 from the tribe of Benjamin were sealed.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>After this I looked, and behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30804H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30804H\"></sup>a great multitude that no one could number, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30804I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30804I\"></sup>from every nation, from all tribes and peoples and languages, standing before the throne and before the Lamb, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30804J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30804J\"></sup>clothed in white robes, with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30804K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30804K\"></sup>palm branches in their hands,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>and crying out with a loud voice, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30805L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30805L\"></sup>“Salvation belongs to our God who sits on the throne, and to the Lamb!”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And all the angels were standing around the throne and around the elders and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30806M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30806M\"></sup>the four living creatures, and they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30806N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30806N\"></sup>fell on their faces before the throne and worshiped God,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30807O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30807O\"></sup>saying, “Amen! Blessing and glory and wisdom and thanksgiving and honor and power and might be to our God forever and ever! Amen.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then one of the elders addressed me, saying, “Who are these, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30808P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30808P\"></sup>clothed in white robes, and from where have they come?”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>I said to him, “Sir, you know.” And he said to me, “These are the ones coming out of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30809Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30809Q\"></sup>the great tribulation. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30809R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30809R\"></sup>They have washed their robes and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30809S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30809S\"></sup>made them white <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30809T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30809T\"></sup>in the blood of the Lamb.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Therefore they are before the throne of God,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30810U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30810U\"></sup>serve him day and night in his temple;and he who sits on the throne <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30810V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30810V\"></sup>will shelter them with his presence.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30811W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30811W\"></sup>They shall hunger no more, neither thirst anymore;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30811X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30811X\"></sup>the sun shall not strike them,nor any scorching heat.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For the Lamb in the midst of the throne <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30812Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30812Y\"></sup>will be their shepherd,and he will guide them to springs of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30812Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30812Z\"></sup>living water,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30812AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30812AA\"></sup>God will wipe away every tear from their eyes.”"
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">8 </span>When the Lamb opened <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30813A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30813A\"></sup>the seventh seal, there was silence in heaven for about half an hour.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Then I saw the seven angels <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30814B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30814B\"></sup>who stand before God, and seven trumpets were given to them.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And another angel came and stood <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30815C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30815C\"></sup>at the altar with a golden censer, and he was given much incense to offer with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30815D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30815D\"></sup>the prayers of all the saints on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30815E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30815E\"></sup>the golden altar before the throne,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30816F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30816F\"></sup>the smoke of the incense, with the prayers of the saints, rose before God from the hand of the angel.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then the angel took the censer and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30817G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30817G\"></sup>filled it with fire from the altar and threw it on the earth, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30817H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30817H\"></sup>there were peals of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30817I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30817I\"></sup>thunder, rumblings, flashes of lightning, and an earthquake.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Now the seven angels who had the seven trumpets prepared to blow them.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>The first angel blew his trumpet, and there followed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30819J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30819J\"></sup>hail and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30819K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30819K\"></sup>fire, mixed with blood, and these were thrown upon the earth. And a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30819L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30819L\"></sup>third of the earth was burned up, and a third of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30819M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30819M\"></sup>the trees were burned up, and all green grass was burned up.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The second angel blew his trumpet, and something like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30820N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30820N\"></sup>a great mountain, burning with fire, was thrown into the sea, and a third of the sea <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30820O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30820O\"></sup>became blood.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>A third of the living creatures in the sea died, and a third of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30821P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30821P\"></sup>the ships were destroyed.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The third angel blew his trumpet, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30822Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30822Q\"></sup>a great star fell from heaven, blazing like a torch, and it fell on a third of the rivers and on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30822R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30822R\"></sup>the springs of water.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>The name of the star is Wormwood. A third of the waters <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30823S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30823S\"></sup>became wormwood, and many people died from the water, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30823T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30823T\"></sup>because it had been made bitter.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The fourth angel blew his trumpet, and a third of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30824U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30824U\"></sup>the sun was struck, and a third of the moon, and a third of the stars, so that a third of their light might be darkened, and a third of the day might be kept from shining, and likewise a third of the night.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then I looked, and I heard an eagle crying with a loud voice as it flew directly overhead, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30825V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30825V\"></sup>“Woe, woe, woe to those who dwell on the earth, at the blasts of the other trumpets that the three angels are about to blow!”"
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">9 </span>And the fifth angel blew his trumpet, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30826A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30826A\"></sup>I saw a star fallen from heaven to earth, and he was given <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30826B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30826B\"></sup>the key to the shaft of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30826C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30826C\"></sup>the bottomless pit.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>He opened the shaft of the bottomless pit, and from the shaft <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30827D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30827D\"></sup>rose smoke like the smoke of a great furnace, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30827E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30827E\"></sup>the sun and the air were darkened with the smoke from the shaft.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then from the smoke came <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30828F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30828F\"></sup>locusts on the earth, and they were given power like the power of scorpions of the earth.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>They were told <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30829G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30829G\"></sup>not to harm <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30829H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30829H\"></sup>the grass of the earth or any green plant or any tree, but only those people who do not have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30829I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30829I\"></sup>the seal of God on their foreheads.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>They were allowed to torment them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30830J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30830J\"></sup>for five months, but not to kill them, and their torment was like the torment of a scorpion when it stings someone.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And in those days <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30831K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30831K\"></sup>people will seek death and will not find it. They will long to die, but death will flee from them.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30832L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30832L\"></sup>In appearance the locusts were like horses prepared for battle: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30832M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30832M\"></sup>on their heads were what looked like crowns of gold; their faces were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30832N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30832N\"></sup>like human faces,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>their hair like women's hair, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30833O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30833O\"></sup>their teeth like lions' teeth;",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>they had breastplates like breastplates of iron, and the noise of their wings was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30834P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30834P\"></sup>like the noise of many chariots with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30834Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30834Q\"></sup>horses rushing into battle.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>They have tails and stings like scorpions, and their power to hurt people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30835R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30835R\"></sup>for five months is in their tails.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>They have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30836S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30836S\"></sup>as king over them the angel of the bottomless pit. His name in Hebrew is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30836T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30836T\"></sup>Abaddon, and in Greek he is called Apollyon.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30837U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30837U\"></sup>The first woe has passed; behold, two woes are still to come.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then the sixth angel blew his trumpet, and I heard a voice from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30838V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30838V\"></sup>the four horns of the golden altar before God,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>saying to the sixth angel who had the trumpet, “Release <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30839W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30839W\"></sup>the four angels who are bound at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30839X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30839X\"></sup>the great river Euphrates.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>So the four angels, who had been prepared for the hour, the day, the month, and the year, were released <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30840Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30840Y\"></sup>to kill a third of mankind.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>The number of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30841Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30841Z\"></sup>mounted troops was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30841AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30841AA\"></sup>twice ten thousand times ten thousand; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30841AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30841AB\"></sup>I heard their number.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And this is how I saw the horses in my vision and those who rode them: they wore breastplates the color of fire and of sapphire and of sulfur, and the heads of the horses were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30842AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30842AC\"></sup>like lions' heads, and fire and smoke and sulfur came out of their mouths.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>By these three plagues a third of mankind was killed, by the fire and smoke and sulfur coming out of their mouths.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>For the power of the horses is in their mouths and in their tails, for their tails are like serpents with heads, and by means of them they wound.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The rest of mankind, who were not killed by these plagues, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30845AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30845AD\"></sup>did not repent of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30845AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30845AE\"></sup>the works of their hands nor give up worshiping <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30845AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30845AF\"></sup>demons <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30845AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30845AG\"></sup>and idols of gold and silver and bronze and stone and wood, which cannot see or hear or walk,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>nor did they repent of their murders or their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30846AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30846AH\"></sup>sorceries or their sexual immorality or their thefts."
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">10 </span>Then I saw another mighty angel coming down from heaven, wrapped in a cloud, with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30847A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30847A\"></sup>a rainbow over his head, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30847B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30847B\"></sup>his face was like the sun, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30847C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30847C\"></sup>his legs like pillars of fire.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30848D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30848D\"></sup>He had a little scroll open in his hand. And he set his right foot on the sea, and his left foot on the land,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and called out with a loud voice, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30849E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30849E\"></sup>like a lion roaring. When he called out, the seven thunders sounded.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And when the seven thunders had sounded, I was about to write, but I heard a voice from heaven saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30850F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30850F\"></sup>“Seal up what the seven thunders have said, and do not write it down.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And the angel whom I saw standing on the sea and on the land <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30851G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30851G\"></sup>raised his right hand to heaven",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>and swore by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30852H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30852H\"></sup>him who lives forever and ever, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30852I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30852I\"></sup>who created heaven and what is in it, the earth and what is in it, and the sea and what is in it, that there would be no more delay,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>but that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30853J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30853J\"></sup>in the days of the trumpet call to be sounded by the seventh angel, the mystery of God would be fulfilled, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30853K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30853K\"></sup>just as he announced to his servants the prophets.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Then the voice that I had heard from heaven spoke to me again, saying, “Go, take the scroll that is open in the hand of the angel who is standing on the sea and on the land.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>So I went to the angel and told him to give me the little scroll. And he said to me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30855L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30855L\"></sup>“Take and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30855M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30855M\"></sup>eat it; it will make your stomach bitter, but in your mouth it will be sweet as honey.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And I took the little scroll from the hand of the angel and ate it. It was sweet as honey in my mouth, but when I had eaten it my stomach was made bitter.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And I was told, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30857N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30857N\"></sup>“You must again prophesy about many peoples and nations and languages and kings.”"
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">11 </span>Then I was given <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30858A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30858A\"></sup>a measuring rod like a staff, and I was told, “Rise and measure the temple of God and the altar and those who worship there,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>but do not measure <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30859B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30859B\"></sup>the court outside the temple; leave that out, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30859C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30859C\"></sup>it is given over to the nations, and they will trample the holy city for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30859D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30859D\"></sup>forty-two months.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And I will grant authority to my two witnesses, and they will prophesy for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30860E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30860E\"></sup>1,260 days, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30860F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30860F\"></sup>clothed in sackcloth.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>These are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30861G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30861G\"></sup>the two olive trees and the two lampstands that stand before the Lord of the earth.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And if anyone would harm them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30862H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30862H\"></sup>fire pours from their mouth and consumes their foes. If anyone would harm them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30862I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30862I\"></sup>this is how he is doomed to be killed.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>They have the power <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30863J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30863J\"></sup>to shut the sky, that no rain may fall during the days of their prophesying, and they have power over the waters to turn them into blood and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30863K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30863K\"></sup>to strike the earth with every kind of plague, as often as they desire.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And when they have finished their testimony, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30864L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30864L\"></sup>the beast that rises from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30864M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30864M\"></sup>the bottomless pit <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30864N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30864N\"></sup>will make war on them and conquer them and kill them,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>and their dead bodies will lie in the street of the great city that symbolically is called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30865O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30865O\"></sup>Sodom and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30865P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30865P\"></sup>Egypt, where their Lord was crucified.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For three and a half days some from the peoples and tribes and languages and nations will gaze at their dead bodies and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30866Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30866Q\"></sup>refuse to let them be placed in a tomb,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30867R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30867R\"></sup>those who dwell on the earth will rejoice over them and make merry and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30867S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30867S\"></sup>exchange presents, because these two prophets <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30867T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30867T\"></sup>had been a torment to those who dwell on the earth.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But after the three and a half days <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30868U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30868U\"></sup>a breath of life from God entered them, and they stood up on their feet, and great fear fell on those who saw them.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then they heard a loud voice from heaven saying to them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30869V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30869V\"></sup>“Come up here!” And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30869W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30869W\"></sup>they went up to heaven <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30869X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30869X\"></sup>in a cloud, and their enemies watched them.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And at that hour there was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30870Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30870Y\"></sup>a great earthquake, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30870Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30870Z\"></sup>a tenth of the city fell. Seven thousand people were killed in the earthquake, and the rest were terrified and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30870AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30870AA\"></sup>gave glory to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30870AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30870AB\"></sup>the God of heaven.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30871AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30871AC\"></sup>The second woe has passed; behold, the third woe is soon to come.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30872AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30872AD\"></sup>the seventh angel blew his trumpet, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30872AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30872AE\"></sup>there were loud voices in heaven, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30872AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30872AF\"></sup>“The kingdom of the world has become the kingdom of our Lord and of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30872AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30872AG\"></sup>his Christ, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30872AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30872AH\"></sup>he shall reign forever and ever.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And the twenty-four elders <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30873AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30873AI\"></sup>who sit on their thrones before God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30873AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30873AJ\"></sup>fell on their faces and worshiped God,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>saying,“We give thanks to you, Lord God Almighty,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30874AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30874AK\"></sup>who is and who was,for you have taken your great powerand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30874AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30874AL\"></sup>begun to reign.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>The nations raged,but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30875AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30875AM\"></sup>your wrath came,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30875AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30875AN\"></sup>the time for the dead to be judged,and for rewarding your servants, the prophets and saints,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30875AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30875AO\"></sup>those who fear your name,both small and great,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30875AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30875AP\"></sup>for destroying the destroyers of the earth.”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30876AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30876AQ\"></sup>God's temple in heaven was opened, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30876AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30876AR\"></sup>the ark of his covenant was seen within his temple. There were flashes of lightning, rumblings, peals of thunder, an earthquake, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30876AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30876AS\"></sup>heavy hail."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">12 </span>And a great sign appeared in heaven: a woman <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30877A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30877A\"></sup>clothed with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30877B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30877B\"></sup>the sun, with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30877C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30877C\"></sup>the moon under her feet, and on her head a crown of twelve stars.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>She was pregnant and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30878D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30878D\"></sup>was crying out in birth pains and the agony of giving birth.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And another sign appeared in heaven: behold, a great <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30879E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30879E\"></sup>red dragon, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30879F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30879F\"></sup>with seven heads and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30879G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30879G\"></sup>ten horns, and on his heads <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30879H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30879H\"></sup>seven diadems.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>His tail swept down <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30880I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30880I\"></sup>a third of the stars of heaven and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30880J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30880J\"></sup>cast them to the earth. And the dragon stood before the woman who was about to give birth, so that when she bore her child <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30880K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30880K\"></sup>he might devour it.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>She gave birth to a male child, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30881L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30881L\"></sup>one who is to rule all the nations with a rod of iron, but her child was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30881M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30881M\"></sup>caught up to God and to his throne,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>and the woman fled into the wilderness, where she has a place prepared by God, in which she is to be nourished for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30882N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30882N\"></sup>1,260 days.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Now war arose in heaven, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30883O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30883O\"></sup>Michael and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30883P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30883P\"></sup>his angels fighting against the dragon. And the dragon and his angels fought back,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>but he was defeated, and there was no longer any place for them in heaven.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30885Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30885Q\"></sup>the great dragon was thrown down, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30885R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30885R\"></sup>that ancient serpent, who is called the devil and Satan, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30885S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30885S\"></sup>the deceiver of the whole world—<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30885T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30885T\"></sup>he was thrown down to the earth, and his angels were thrown down with him.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And I heard a loud voice in heaven, saying, “Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30886U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30886U\"></sup>the salvation and the power and the kingdom of our God and the authority of his Christ have come, for the accuser of our brothers has been thrown down, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30886V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30886V\"></sup>who accuses them day and night before our God.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30887W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30887W\"></sup>they have conquered him by the blood of the Lamb and by the word of their testimony, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30887X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30887X\"></sup>they loved not their lives <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30887Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30887Y\"></sup>even unto death.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Therefore, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30888Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30888Z\"></sup>rejoice, O heavens and you who dwell in them! But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30888AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30888AA\"></sup>woe to you, O earth and sea, for the devil has come down to you in great wrath, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30888AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30888AB\"></sup>he knows that his time is short!”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And when the dragon saw that he had been thrown down to the earth, he pursued <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30889AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30889AC\"></sup>the woman who had given birth to the male child.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But the woman was given the two <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30890AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30890AD\"></sup>wings of the great eagle so that she might fly from the serpent <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30890AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30890AE\"></sup>into the wilderness, to the place where she is to be nourished <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30890AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30890AF\"></sup>for a time, and times, and half a time.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The serpent poured water <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30891AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30891AG\"></sup>like a river out of his mouth after the woman, to sweep her away with a flood.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But the earth came to the help of the woman, and the earth opened its mouth and swallowed the river that the dragon had poured from his mouth.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Then the dragon became furious with the woman and went off <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30893AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30893AH\"></sup>to make war on the rest of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30893AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30893AI\"></sup>her offspring, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30893AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30893AJ\"></sup>on those who keep the commandments of God and hold to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30893AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30893AK\"></sup>the testimony of Jesus. And he stood on the sand of the sea."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">13 </span>And I saw a beast rising out of the sea, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30894A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30894A\"></sup>with ten horns and seven heads, with ten diadems on its horns and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30894B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30894B\"></sup>blasphemous names on its heads.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And the beast that I saw was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30895C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30895C\"></sup>like a leopard; its feet were like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30895D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30895D\"></sup>a bear's, and its mouth was like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30895E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30895E\"></sup>a lion's mouth. And to it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30895F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30895F\"></sup>the dragon gave his power and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30895G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30895G\"></sup>his throne and great authority.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>One of its heads seemed to have a mortal wound, but its mortal wound was healed, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30896H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30896H\"></sup>the whole earth marveled as they followed the beast.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And they worshiped the dragon, for he had given his authority to the beast, and they worshiped the beast, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30897I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30897I\"></sup>“Who is like the beast, and who can fight against it?”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And the beast was given <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30898J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30898J\"></sup>a mouth uttering haughty and blasphemous words, and it was allowed to exercise authority for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30898K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30898K\"></sup>forty-two months.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>It opened its mouth to utter blasphemies against God, blaspheming his name and his dwelling, that is, those who dwell in heaven.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Also it was allowed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30900L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30900L\"></sup>to make war on the saints and to conquer them. And authority was given it over every tribe and people and language and nation,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>and all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30901M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30901M\"></sup>who dwell on earth will worship it, everyone whose name has not been written before the foundation of the world in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30901N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30901N\"></sup>the book of life of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30901O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30901O\"></sup>the Lamb <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30901P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30901P\"></sup>who was slain.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30902Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30902Q\"></sup>If anyone has an ear, let him hear:",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30903R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30903R\"></sup>If anyone is to be taken captive,to captivity he goes;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30903S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30903S\"></sup>if anyone is to be slain with the sword,with the sword must he be slain.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30903T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30903T\"></sup>Here is a call for the endurance and faith of the saints.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30904U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30904U\"></sup>I saw another beast rising out of the earth. It had two horns like a lamb and it spoke like a dragon.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>It exercises all the authority of the first beast in its presence, and makes the earth and its inhabitants worship the first beast, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30905V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30905V\"></sup>whose mortal wound was healed.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30906W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30906W\"></sup>It performs great signs, even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30906X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30906X\"></sup>making fire come down from heaven to earth in front of people,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>and by the signs that it is allowed to work in the presence of the beast <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30907Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30907Y\"></sup>it deceives those who dwell on earth, telling them to make an image for the beast <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30907Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30907Z\"></sup>that was wounded by the sword and yet lived.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And it was allowed to give breath to the image of the beast, so that the image of the beast might even speak and might cause those who would not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30908AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30908AA\"></sup>worship the image of the beast <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30908AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30908AB\"></sup>to be slain.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Also it causes all, both small and great, both rich and poor, both free and slave, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30909AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30909AC\"></sup>to be marked on the right hand or the forehead,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>so that no one can buy or sell unless he has the mark, that is, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30910AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30910AD\"></sup>the name of the beast or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30910AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30910AE\"></sup>the number of its name.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30911AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30911AF\"></sup>This calls for wisdom: let the one who has understanding calculate the number of the beast, for it is the number <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30911AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30911AG\"></sup>of a man, and his number is 666."
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">14 </span>Then I looked, and behold, on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30912A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30912A\"></sup>Mount Zion <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30912B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30912B\"></sup>stood the Lamb, and with him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30912C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30912C\"></sup>144,000 who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30912D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30912D\"></sup>had his name and his Father's name written <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30912E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30912E\"></sup>on their foreheads.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And I heard a voice from heaven <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30913F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30913F\"></sup>like the roar of many waters and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30913G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30913G\"></sup>like the sound of loud thunder. The voice I heard was like the sound of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30913H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30913H\"></sup>harpists playing on their harps,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and they were singing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30914I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30914I\"></sup>a new song before the throne and before the four living creatures and before the elders. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30914J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30914J\"></sup>No one could learn that song except the 144,000 who had been redeemed from the earth.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>It is these who have not defiled themselves with women, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30915K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30915K\"></sup>they are virgins. It is these <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30915L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30915L\"></sup>who follow the Lamb wherever he goes. These have been redeemed from mankind as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30915M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30915M\"></sup>firstfruits for God and the Lamb,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30916N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30916N\"></sup>in their mouth no lie was found, for they are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30916O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30916O\"></sup>blameless.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Then I saw another angel <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30917P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30917P\"></sup>flying directly overhead, with an eternal gospel to proclaim to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30917Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30917Q\"></sup>those who dwell on earth, to every nation and tribe and language and people.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And he said with a loud voice, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30918R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30918R\"></sup>“Fear God and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30918S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30918S\"></sup>give him glory, because the hour of his judgment has come, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30918T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30918T\"></sup>worship him who made heaven and earth, the sea and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30918U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30918U\"></sup>springs of water.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Another angel, a second, followed, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30919V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30919V\"></sup>“Fallen, fallen is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30919W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30919W\"></sup>Babylon the great, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30919X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30919X\"></sup>she who made all nations drink <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30919Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30919Y\"></sup>the wine of the passion of her sexual immorality.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And another angel, a third, followed them, saying with a loud voice, “If anyone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30920Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30920Z\"></sup>worships the beast and its image and receives <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30920AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30920AA\"></sup>a mark on his forehead or on his hand,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>he also will drink <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30921AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30921AB\"></sup>the wine of God's wrath, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30921AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30921AC\"></sup>poured full strength into the cup of his anger, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30921AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30921AD\"></sup>he will be tormented with fire and sulfur in the presence of the holy angels and in the presence of the Lamb.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30922AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30922AE\"></sup>the smoke of their torment goes up forever and ever, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30922AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30922AF\"></sup>they have no rest, day or night, these <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30922AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30922AG\"></sup>worshipers of the beast and its image, and whoever receives the mark of its name.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30923AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30923AH\"></sup>Here is a call for the endurance of the saints, those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30923AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30923AI\"></sup>keep the commandments of God and their faith in Jesus.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And I heard a voice from heaven saying, “Write this: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30924AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30924AJ\"></sup>Blessed are the dead <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30924AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30924AK\"></sup>who die in the Lord from now on.” “Blessed indeed,” says the Spirit, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30924AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30924AL\"></sup>“that they may rest from their labors, for their deeds follow them!”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Then I looked, and behold, a white cloud, and seated on the cloud one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30925AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30925AM\"></sup>like a son of man, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30925AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30925AN\"></sup>with a golden crown on his head, and a sharp sickle in his hand.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And another angel <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30926AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30926AO\"></sup>came out of the temple, calling with a loud voice to him who sat on the cloud, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30926AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30926AP\"></sup>“Put in your sickle, and reap, for the hour to reap has come, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30926AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30926AQ\"></sup>the harvest of the earth is fully ripe.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>So he who sat on the cloud swung his sickle across the earth, and the earth was reaped.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Then another angel came out of the temple in heaven, and he too had a sharp sickle.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And another angel came out from the altar, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30929AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30929AR\"></sup>the angel who has authority over the fire, and he called with a loud voice to the one who had the sharp sickle, “Put in your sickle and gather the clusters from the vine of the earth, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30929AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30929AS\"></sup>for its grapes are ripe.”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>So the angel swung his sickle across the earth and gathered the grape harvest of the earth and threw it into the great <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30930AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30930AT\"></sup>winepress of the wrath of God.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30931AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30931AU\"></sup>the winepress was trodden <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30931AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30931AV\"></sup>outside the city, and blood flowed from the winepress, as high as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30931AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30931AW\"></sup>a horse's bridle, for 1,600 stadia."
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">15 </span>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30932A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30932A\"></sup>I saw another sign in heaven, great and amazing, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30932B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30932B\"></sup>seven angels with seven plagues, which are the last, for with them the wrath of God is finished.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And I saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30933C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30933C\"></sup>what appeared to be a sea of glass mingled with fire—and also those <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30933D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30933D\"></sup>who had conquered the beast and its image and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30933E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30933E\"></sup>the number of its name, standing beside the sea of glass <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30933F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30933F\"></sup>with harps of God in their hands.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And they sing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30934G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30934G\"></sup>the song of Moses, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30934H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30934H\"></sup>the servant of God, and the song of the Lamb, saying,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30934I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30934I\"></sup>“Great and amazing are your deeds,O Lord God the Almighty!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30934J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30934J\"></sup>Just and true are your ways,O King of the nations!",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30935K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30935K\"></sup>Who will not fear, O Lord,and glorify your name?For you alone are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30935L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30935L\"></sup>holy.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30935M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30935M\"></sup>All nations will comeand worship you,for your righteous acts have been revealed.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>After this I looked, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30936N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30936N\"></sup>the sanctuary of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30936O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30936O\"></sup>the tent of witness in heaven was opened,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>and out of the sanctuary came <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30937P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30937P\"></sup>the seven angels with the seven plagues, clothed in pure, bright <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30937Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30937Q\"></sup>linen, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30937R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30937R\"></sup>with golden sashes around their chests.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And one of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30938S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30938S\"></sup>the four living creatures gave to the seven angels seven <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30938T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30938T\"></sup>golden bowls full of the wrath of God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30938U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30938U\"></sup>who lives forever and ever,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30939V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30939V\"></sup>the sanctuary was filled with smoke from the glory of God and from his power, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30939W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30939W\"></sup>no one could enter the sanctuary until the seven plagues of the seven angels were finished."
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">16 </span>Then I heard a loud voice from the temple telling <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30940A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30940A\"></sup>the seven angels, “Go and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30940B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30940B\"></sup>pour out on the earth <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30940C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30940C\"></sup>the seven bowls of the wrath of God.”",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>So the first angel went and poured out his bowl on the earth, and harmful and painful <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30941D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30941D\"></sup>sores came upon the people who bore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30941E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30941E\"></sup>the mark of the beast and worshiped its image.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>The second angel poured out his bowl into the sea, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30942F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30942F\"></sup>it became like the blood of a corpse, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30942G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30942G\"></sup>every living thing died that was in the sea.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The third angel poured out his bowl into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30943H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30943H\"></sup>the rivers and the springs of water, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30943I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30943I\"></sup>they became blood.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And I heard the angel in charge of the waters say,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30944J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30944J\"></sup>“Just are you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30944K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30944K\"></sup>O Holy One, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30944L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30944L\"></sup>who is and who was,for you brought these judgments.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30945M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30945M\"></sup>they have shed the blood of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30945N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30945N\"></sup>saints and prophets,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30945O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30945O\"></sup>you have given them blood to drink.It is what they deserve!”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And I heard <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30946P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30946P\"></sup>the altar saying,“Yes, Lord God the Almighty,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30946Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30946Q\"></sup>true and just are your judgments!”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The fourth angel poured out his bowl on the sun, and it was allowed to scorch people <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30947R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30947R\"></sup>with fire.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>They were scorched by the fierce heat, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30948S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30948S\"></sup>they cursed the name of God who had power over these plagues. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30948T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30948T\"></sup>They did not repent <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30948U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30948U\"></sup>and give him glory.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The fifth angel poured out his bowl on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30949V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30949V\"></sup>the throne of the beast, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30949W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30949W\"></sup>its kingdom was plunged into darkness. People gnawed their tongues in anguish",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>and cursed <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30950X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30950X\"></sup>the God of heaven for their pain and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30950Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30950Y\"></sup>sores. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30950Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30950Z\"></sup>They did not repent of their deeds.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>The sixth angel poured out his bowl on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30951AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30951AA\"></sup>the great river Euphrates, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30951AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30951AB\"></sup>its water was dried up, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30951AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30951AC\"></sup>to prepare the way for the kings <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30951AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30951AD\"></sup>from the east.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And I saw, coming out of the mouth of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30952AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30952AE\"></sup>the dragon and out of the mouth of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30952AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30952AF\"></sup>the beast and out of the mouth of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30952AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30952AG\"></sup>the false prophet, three <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30952AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30952AH\"></sup>unclean spirits like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30952AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30952AI\"></sup>frogs.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For they are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30953AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30953AJ\"></sup>demonic spirits, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30953AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30953AK\"></sup>performing signs, who go abroad to the kings of the whole world, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30953AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30953AL\"></sup>to assemble them for battle on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30953AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30953AM\"></sup>the great day of God the Almighty.",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>(“Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30954AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30954AN\"></sup>I am coming like a thief! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30954AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30954AO\"></sup>Blessed is the one who stays awake, keeping his garments on, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30954AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30954AP\"></sup>that he may not go about naked and be seen exposed!”)</span>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30955AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30955AQ\"></sup>they assembled them at the place that in Hebrew is called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30955AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30955AR\"></sup>Armageddon.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>The seventh angel poured out his bowl into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30956AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30956AS\"></sup>the air, and a loud voice came out of the temple, from the throne, saying, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30956AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30956AT\"></sup>“It is done!”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And there were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30957AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30957AU\"></sup>flashes of lightning, rumblings, peals of thunder, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30957AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30957AV\"></sup>a great earthquake <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30957AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30957AW\"></sup>such as there had never been since man was on the earth, so great was that earthquake.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30958AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30958AX\"></sup>The great city <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30958AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30958AY\"></sup>was split into three parts, and the cities of the nations fell, and God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30958AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30958AZ\"></sup>remembered <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30958BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30958BA\"></sup>Babylon the great, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30958BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30958BB\"></sup>to make her drain the cup of the wine of the fury of his wrath.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30959BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30959BC\"></sup>every island fled away, and no mountains were to be found.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30960BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30960BD\"></sup>great hailstones, about one hundred pounds each, fell from heaven on people; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30960BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30960BE\"></sup>they cursed God for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30960BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30960BF\"></sup>the plague of the hail, because the plague was so severe."
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">17 </span>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30961A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30961A\"></sup>one of the seven angels who had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30961B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30961B\"></sup>the seven bowls came and said to me, “Come, I will show you the judgment of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30961C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30961C\"></sup>the great prostitute <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30961D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30961D\"></sup>who is seated on many waters,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30962E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30962E\"></sup>with whom the kings of the earth have committed sexual immorality, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30962F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30962F\"></sup>with the wine of whose sexual immorality <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30962G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30962G\"></sup>the dwellers on earth have become drunk.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30963H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30963H\"></sup>he carried me away in the Spirit <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30963I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30963I\"></sup>into a wilderness, and I saw a woman sitting on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30963J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30963J\"></sup>a scarlet beast that was full of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30963K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30963K\"></sup>blasphemous names, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30963L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30963L\"></sup>it had seven heads and ten horns.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The woman <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30964M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30964M\"></sup>was arrayed in purple and scarlet, and adorned <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30964N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30964N\"></sup>with gold and jewels and pearls, holding in her hand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30964O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30964O\"></sup>a golden cup full of abominations and the impurities of her sexual immorality.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And on her forehead was written a name of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30965P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30965P\"></sup>mystery: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30965Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30965Q\"></sup>“Babylon the great, mother of prostitutes and of earth's abominations.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And I saw the woman, drunk <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30966R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30966R\"></sup>with the blood of the saints, the blood of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30966S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30966S\"></sup>the martyrs of Jesus.When I saw her, I marveled greatly.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But the angel said to me, “Why do you marvel? I will tell you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30967T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30967T\"></sup>the mystery of the woman, and of the beast with seven heads and ten horns that carries her.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The beast that you saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30968U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30968U\"></sup>was, and is not, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30968V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30968V\"></sup>is about to rise from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30968W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30968W\"></sup>the bottomless pit and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30968X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30968X\"></sup>go to destruction. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30968Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30968Y\"></sup>the dwellers on earth whose names have not been written in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30968Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30968Z\"></sup>the book of life from the foundation of the world will marvel to see the beast, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30968AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30968AA\"></sup>it was and is not and is to come.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30969AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30969AB\"></sup>This calls for a mind with wisdom: the seven heads are seven mountains on which the woman is seated;",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>they are also seven kings, five of whom have fallen, one is, the other has not yet come, and when he does come he must remain only a little while.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>As for the beast <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30971AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30971AC\"></sup>that was and is not, it is an eighth but it belongs to the seven, and it goes to destruction.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30972AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30972AD\"></sup>the ten horns that you saw are ten kings who have not yet received royal power, but they are to receive authority as kings <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30972AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30972AE\"></sup>for one hour, together with the beast.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>These are of one mind, and they hand over their power and authority to the beast.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30974AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30974AF\"></sup>will make war on the Lamb, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30974AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30974AG\"></sup>the Lamb will conquer them, for he is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30974AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30974AH\"></sup>Lord of lords and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30974AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30974AI\"></sup>King of kings, and those with him are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30974AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30974AJ\"></sup>called and chosen and faithful.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And the angel said to me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30975AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30975AK\"></sup>“The waters that you saw, where the prostitute is seated, are peoples and multitudes and nations and languages.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30976AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30976AL\"></sup>the ten horns that you saw, they and the beast <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30976AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30976AM\"></sup>will hate the prostitute. They will make her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30976AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30976AN\"></sup>desolate and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30976AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30976AO\"></sup>naked, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30976AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30976AP\"></sup>devour her flesh and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30976AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30976AQ\"></sup>burn her up with fire,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30977AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30977AR\"></sup>God has put it into their hearts to carry out his purpose by being of one mind and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30977AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30977AS\"></sup>handing over their royal power to the beast, until the words of God are fulfilled.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And the woman that you saw is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30978AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30978AT\"></sup>the great city that has dominion over the kings of the earth.”"
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">18 </span>After this I saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30979A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30979A\"></sup>another angel coming down from heaven, having great authority, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30979B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30979B\"></sup>the earth was made bright with his glory.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And he called out with a mighty voice,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30980C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30980C\"></sup>“Fallen, fallen is Babylon the great!She has become <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30980D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30980D\"></sup>a dwelling place for demons,a haunt <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30980E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30980E\"></sup>for every unclean spirit,a haunt <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30980F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30980F\"></sup>for every unclean bird,a haunt for every unclean and detestable beast.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For all nations have drunk<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30981G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30981G\"></sup>the wine of the passion of her sexual immorality,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30981H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30981H\"></sup>the kings of the earth have committed immorality with her,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30981I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30981I\"></sup>the merchants of the earth have grown rich from the power of her luxurious living.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then I heard another voice from heaven saying,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30982J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30982J\"></sup>“Come out of her, my people,lest you take part in her sins,lest you share in her plagues;",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30983K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30983K\"></sup>her sins are heaped high as heaven,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30983L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30983L\"></sup>God has remembered her iniquities.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30984M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30984M\"></sup>Pay her back as she herself has paid back others,and repay her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30984N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30984N\"></sup>double for her deeds;mix a double portion for her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30984O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30984O\"></sup>in the cup she mixed.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30985P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30985P\"></sup>As she glorified herself and lived in luxury,so give her a like measure of torment and mourning,since in her heart she says,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30985Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30985Q\"></sup>‘I sit as a queen,I am no widow,and mourning I shall never see.’",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For this reason her plagues will come <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30986R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30986R\"></sup>in a single day,death and mourning and famine,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30986S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30986S\"></sup>she will be burned up with fire;for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30986T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30986T\"></sup>mighty is the Lord God who has judged her.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30987U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30987U\"></sup>the kings of the earth, who committed sexual immorality and lived in luxury with her, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30987V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30987V\"></sup>will weep and wail over her <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30987W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30987W\"></sup>when they see the smoke of her burning.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30988X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30988X\"></sup>They will stand far off, in fear of her torment, and say,“Alas! Alas! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30988Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30988Y\"></sup>You great city,you mighty city, Babylon!For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30988Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30988Z\"></sup>in a single hour your judgment has come.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30989AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30989AA\"></sup>the merchants of the earth weep and mourn for her, since no one buys their cargo anymore,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>cargo of gold, silver, jewels, pearls, fine linen, purple cloth, silk, scarlet cloth, all kinds of scented wood, all kinds of articles of ivory, all kinds of articles of costly wood, bronze, iron and marble,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>cinnamon, spice, incense, myrrh, frankincense, wine, oil, fine flour, wheat, cattle and sheep, horses and chariots, and slaves, that is, human souls.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“The fruit for which your soul longedhas gone from you,and all your delicacies and your splendorsare lost to you,never to be found again!”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30993AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30993AB\"></sup>The merchants of these wares, who gained wealth from her, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30993AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30993AC\"></sup>will stand far off, in fear of her torment, weeping and mourning aloud,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“Alas, alas, for the great city<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30994AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30994AD\"></sup>that was clothed in fine linen,in purple and scarlet,adorned with gold,with jewels, and with pearls!",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30995AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30995AE\"></sup>in a single hour all this wealth <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30995AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30995AF\"></sup>has been laid waste.”And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30995AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30995AG\"></sup>all shipmasters and seafaring men, sailors and all whose trade is on the sea, stood far off",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30996AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30996AH\"></sup>cried out <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30996AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30996AI\"></sup>as they saw the smoke of her burning,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30996AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30996AJ\"></sup>“What city was like the great city?”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And they threw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30997AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30997AK\"></sup>dust on their heads as they wept and mourned, crying out,“Alas, alas, for the great city<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30997AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30997AL\"></sup>where all who had ships at seagrew rich by her wealth!For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30997AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30997AM\"></sup>in a single hour she has been laid waste.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30998AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30998AN\"></sup>Rejoice over her, O heaven,and you saints and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30998AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30998AO\"></sup>apostles and prophets,for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30998AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30998AP\"></sup>God has given judgment for you against her!”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30999AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30999AQ\"></sup>a mighty angel <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30999AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30999AR\"></sup>took up a stone like a great millstone and threw it into the sea, saying,“So will Babylon <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-30999AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-30999AS\"></sup>the great city be thrown down with violence,and will be found no more;",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31000AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31000AT\"></sup>the sound of harpists and musicians, of flute players and trumpeters,will be heard in you no more,and a craftsman of any craftwill be found in you no more,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31000AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31000AU\"></sup>the sound of the millwill be heard in you no more,",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>and the light of a lampwill shine in you no more,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31001AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31001AV\"></sup>the voice of bridegroom and bridewill be heard in you no more,for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31001AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31001AW\"></sup>your merchants were the great ones of the earth,and all nations were deceived <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31001AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31001AX\"></sup>by your sorcery.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31002AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31002AY\"></sup>in her was found the blood of prophets and of saints,and of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31002AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31002AZ\"></sup>all who have been slain on earth.”"
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">19 </span>After this I heard <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31003A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31003A\"></sup>what seemed to be the loud voice of a great multitude in heaven, crying out,“Hallelujah!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31003B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31003B\"></sup>Salvation and glory and power belong to our God,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><span class=\"indent-1-breaks\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31004C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31004C\"></sup>his judgments are true and just;for he has judged <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31004D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31004D\"></sup>the great prostitutewho corrupted the earth with her immorality,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31004E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31004E\"></sup>has avenged on her the blood of his servants.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Once more they cried out,“Hallelujah!<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31005F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31005F\"></sup>The smoke from her goes up forever and ever.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31006G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31006G\"></sup>the twenty-four elders and the four living creatures fell down and worshiped God who was seated on the throne, saying, “Amen. Hallelujah!”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And from the throne came a voice saying,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31007H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31007H\"></sup>“Praise our God,all you his servants,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31007I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31007I\"></sup>you who fear him,small and great.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Then I heard what seemed to be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31008J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31008J\"></sup>the voice of a great multitude, like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31008K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31008K\"></sup>the roar of many waters and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31008L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31008L\"></sup>like the sound of mighty peals of thunder, crying out,“Hallelujah!For the Lord our Godthe Almighty <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31008M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31008M\"></sup>reigns.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Let us rejoice and exultand give him the glory,for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31009N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31009N\"></sup>the marriage of the Lamb has come,and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31009O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31009O\"></sup>his Bride has made herself ready;",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31010P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31010P\"></sup>it was granted her to clothe herselfwith fine linen, bright and pure”—for the fine linen is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31010Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31010Q\"></sup>the righteous deeds of the saints.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And the angel said to me, “Write this: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31011R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31011R\"></sup>Blessed are those who are invited to the marriage supper of the Lamb.” And he said to me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31011S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31011S\"></sup>“These are the true words of God.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31012T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31012T\"></sup>I fell down at his feet to worship him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31012U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31012U\"></sup>but he said to me, “You must not do that! I am a fellow servant with you and your brothers who hold to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31012V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31012V\"></sup>the testimony of Jesus. Worship God.” For the testimony of Jesus is the spirit of prophecy.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then I saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31013W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31013W\"></sup>heaven opened, and behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31013X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31013X\"></sup>a white horse! The one sitting on it is called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31013Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31013Y\"></sup>Faithful and True, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31013Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31013Z\"></sup>in righteousness he judges and makes war.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31014AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31014AA\"></sup>His eyes are like a flame of fire, and on his head are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31014AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31014AB\"></sup>many diadems, and he has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31014AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31014AC\"></sup>a name written that no one knows but himself.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>He is clothed in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31015AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31015AD\"></sup>a robe dipped in blood, and the name by which he is called is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31015AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31015AE\"></sup>The Word of God.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And the armies of heaven, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31016AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31016AF\"></sup>arrayed in fine linen, white and pure, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31016AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31016AG\"></sup>were following him on white horses.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31017AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31017AH\"></sup>From his mouth comes a sharp sword <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31017AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31017AI\"></sup>with which to strike down the nations, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31017AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31017AJ\"></sup>he will rule them with a rod of iron. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31017AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31017AK\"></sup>He will tread the winepress of the fury of the wrath of God the Almighty.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>On his robe and on his thigh <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31018AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31018AL\"></sup>he has a name written, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31018AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31018AM\"></sup>King of kings and Lord of lords.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Then I saw an angel standing in the sun, and with a loud voice he called to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31019AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31019AN\"></sup>all the birds that fly directly overhead, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31019AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31019AO\"></sup>“Come, gather for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31019AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31019AP\"></sup>the great supper of God,",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31020AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31020AQ\"></sup>to eat the flesh of kings, the flesh of captains, the flesh of mighty men, the flesh of horses and their riders, and the flesh of all men, both free and slave, both small and great.”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And I saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31021AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31021AR\"></sup>the beast and the kings of the earth with their armies <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31021AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31021AS\"></sup>gathered to make war against him who was sitting on the horse and against his army.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And the beast was captured, and with it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31022AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31022AT\"></sup>the false prophet <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31022AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31022AU\"></sup>who in its presence had done the signs by which he deceived those who had received the mark of the beast and those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31022AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31022AV\"></sup>worshiped its image. These two were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31022AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31022AW\"></sup>thrown alive into the lake of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31022AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31022AX\"></sup>fire that burns with sulfur.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And the rest were slain by the sword <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31023AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31023AY\"></sup>that came from the mouth of him who was sitting on the horse, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31023AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31023AZ\"></sup>all the birds were gorged with their flesh."
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">20 </span>Then I saw an angel coming down from heaven, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31024A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31024A\"></sup>holding in his hand the key to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31024B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31024B\"></sup>the bottomless pit and a great chain.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And he seized <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31025C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31025C\"></sup>the dragon, that ancient serpent, who is the devil and Satan, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31025D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31025D\"></sup>bound him for a thousand years,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and threw him into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31026E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31026E\"></sup>the pit, and shut it and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31026F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31026F\"></sup>sealed it over him, so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31026G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31026G\"></sup>he might not deceive the nations any longer, until the thousand years were ended. After that he must be released for a little while.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Then I saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31027H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31027H\"></sup>thrones, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31027I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31027I\"></sup>seated on them were those to whom the authority to judge was committed. Also I saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31027J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31027J\"></sup>the souls of those who had been beheaded for the testimony of Jesus and for the word of God, and those <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31027K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31027K\"></sup>who had not worshiped the beast or its image and had not received its mark on their foreheads or their hands. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31027L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31027L\"></sup>They came to life and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31027M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31027M\"></sup>reigned with Christ for a thousand years.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The rest of the dead did not come to life until the thousand years were ended. This is the first resurrection.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31029N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31029N\"></sup>Blessed and holy is the one who shares in the first resurrection! Over such <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31029O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31029O\"></sup>the second death has no power, but they will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31029P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31029P\"></sup>priests of God and of Christ, and they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31029Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31029Q\"></sup>will reign with him for a thousand years.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And when the thousand years are ended, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31030R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31030R\"></sup>Satan will be released from his prison",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>and will come out <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31031S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31031S\"></sup>to deceive the nations that are at the four corners of the earth, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31031T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31031T\"></sup>Gog and Magog, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31031U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31031U\"></sup>to gather them for battle; their number is like the sand of the sea.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31032V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31032V\"></sup>they marched up over the broad plain of the earth and surrounded <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31032W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31032W\"></sup>the camp of the saints and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31032X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31032X\"></sup>the beloved city, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31032Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31032Y\"></sup>fire came down from heaven and consumed them,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>and the devil <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31033Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31033Z\"></sup>who had deceived them was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31033AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31033AA\"></sup>thrown into the lake of fire and sulfur where <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31033AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31033AB\"></sup>the beast and the false prophet were, and they will be tormented day and night forever and ever.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then I saw a great white throne and him who was seated on it. From his presence <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31034AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31034AC\"></sup>earth and sky fled away, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31034AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31034AD\"></sup>no place was found for them.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And I saw the dead, great and small, standing before the throne, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31035AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31035AE\"></sup>books were opened. Then another book was opened, which is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31035AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31035AF\"></sup>the book of life. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31035AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31035AG\"></sup>the dead were judged by what was written in the books, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31035AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31035AH\"></sup>according to what they had done.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And the sea gave up the dead who were in it, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31036AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31036AI\"></sup>Death and Hades gave up the dead who were in them, and they were judged, each one of them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31036AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31036AJ\"></sup>according to what they had done.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31037AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31037AK\"></sup>Death and Hades <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31037AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31037AL\"></sup>were thrown into the lake of fire. This is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31037AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31037AM\"></sup>the second death, the lake of fire.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And if anyone's name was not found written in the book of life, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31038AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31038AN\"></sup>he was thrown into the lake of fire."
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">21 </span>Then I saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31039A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31039A\"></sup>a new heaven and a new earth, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31039B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31039B\"></sup>the first heaven and the first earth had passed away, and the sea was no more.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And I saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31040C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31040C\"></sup>the holy city, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31040D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31040D\"></sup>new Jerusalem, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31040E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31040E\"></sup>coming down out of heaven from God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31040F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31040F\"></sup>prepared <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31040G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31040G\"></sup>as a bride adorned for her husband.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And I heard a loud voice from the throne saying, “Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31041H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31041H\"></sup>the dwelling place of God is with man. He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31041I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31041I\"></sup>dwell with them, and they will be his people, and God himself will be with them as their God.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31042J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31042J\"></sup>He will wipe away every tear from their eyes, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31042K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31042K\"></sup>death shall be no more, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31042L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31042L\"></sup>neither shall there be mourning, nor crying, nor pain anymore, for the former things have passed away.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31043M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31043M\"></sup>he who was seated on the throne said, “Behold, I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31043N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31043N\"></sup>am making all things new.” Also he said, “Write this down, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31043O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31043O\"></sup>these words are trustworthy and true.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And he said to me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31044P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31044P\"></sup>“It is done! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31044Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31044Q\"></sup>I am the Alpha and the Omega, the beginning and the end. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31044R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31044R\"></sup>To the thirsty I will give from the spring of the water of life without payment.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31045S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31045S\"></sup>The one who conquers will have this heritage, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31045T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31045T\"></sup>I will be his God and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31045U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31045U\"></sup>he will be my son.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31046V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31046V\"></sup>But as for the cowardly, the faithless, the detestable, as for murderers, the sexually immoral, sorcerers, idolaters, and all liars, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31046W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31046W\"></sup>their portion will be in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31046X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31046X\"></sup>the lake that burns with fire and sulfur, which is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31046Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31046Y\"></sup>the second death.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then came <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31047Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31047Z\"></sup>one of the seven angels who had the seven bowls full of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31047AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31047AA\"></sup>the seven last plagues and spoke to me, saying, “Come, I will show you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31047AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31047AB\"></sup>the Bride, the wife of the Lamb.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31048AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31048AC\"></sup>he carried me away in the Spirit to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31048AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31048AD\"></sup>a great, high mountain, and showed me the holy city Jerusalem coming down out of heaven from God,",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31049AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31049AE\"></sup>having the glory of God, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31049AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31049AF\"></sup>its radiance <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31049AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31049AG\"></sup>like a most rare jewel, like a jasper, clear as crystal.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>It had a great, high wall, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31050AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31050AH\"></sup>with twelve gates, and at the gates twelve angels, and on the gates the names of the twelve tribes of the sons of Israel were inscribed—",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>on the east three gates, on the north three gates, on the south three gates, and on the west three gates.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And the wall of the city had twelve <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31052AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31052AI\"></sup>foundations, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31052AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31052AJ\"></sup>on them were the twelve names of the twelve apostles of the Lamb.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And the one who spoke with me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31053AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31053AK\"></sup>had a measuring rod of gold to measure the city and its gates and walls.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>The city lies foursquare, its length the same as its width. And he measured the city with his rod, 12,000 stadia. Its length and width and height are equal.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>He also measured its wall, 144 cubits by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31055AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31055AL\"></sup>human measurement, which is also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31055AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31055AM\"></sup>an angel's measurement.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>The wall was built of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31056AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31056AN\"></sup>jasper, while the city was pure gold, like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31056AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31056AO\"></sup>clear glass.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31057AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31057AP\"></sup>The foundations of the wall of the city were adorned with every kind of jewel. The first was jasper, the second sapphire, the third agate, the fourth emerald,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>the fifth onyx, the sixth carnelian, the seventh chrysolite, the eighth beryl, the ninth topaz, the tenth chrysoprase, the eleventh jacinth, the twelfth amethyst.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And the twelve gates were twelve pearls, each of the gates made of a single pearl, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31059AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31059AQ\"></sup>the street of the city was pure gold, like transparent glass.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31060AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31060AR\"></sup>I saw no temple in the city, for its temple is the Lord God the Almighty and the Lamb.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And the city <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31061AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31061AS\"></sup>has no need of sun or moon to shine on it, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31061AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31061AT\"></sup>the glory of God gives it light, and its lamp is the Lamb.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>By its light <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31062AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31062AU\"></sup>will the nations walk, and the kings of the earth <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31062AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31062AV\"></sup>will bring their glory into it,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31063AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31063AW\"></sup>its gates will never be shut by day—and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31063AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31063AX\"></sup>there will be no night there.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>They will bring into it the glory and the honor of the nations.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31065AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31065AY\"></sup>nothing unclean will ever enter it, nor anyone who does what is detestable or false, but only those who are written in the Lamb's <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31065AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31065AZ\"></sup>book of life."
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">22 </span>Then the angel showed me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31066A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31066A\"></sup>the river of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31066B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31066B\"></sup>the water of life, bright as crystal, flowing from the throne of God and of the Lamb",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>through the middle of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31067C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31067C\"></sup>the street of the city; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31067D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31067D\"></sup>also, on either side of the river, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31067E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31067E\"></sup>the tree of life with its twelve kinds of fruit, yielding its fruit each month. The leaves of the tree were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31067F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31067F\"></sup>for the healing of the nations.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31068G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31068G\"></sup>No longer will there be anything accursed, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31068H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31068H\"></sup>the throne of God and of the Lamb will be in it, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31068I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31068I\"></sup>his servants will worship him.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31069J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31069J\"></sup>They will see his face, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31069K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31069K\"></sup>his name will be on their foreheads.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31070L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31070L\"></sup>night will be no more. They will need no light of lamp <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31070M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31070M\"></sup>or sun, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31070N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31070N\"></sup>the Lord God will be their light, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31070O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31070O\"></sup>they will reign forever and ever.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And he said to me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31071P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31071P\"></sup>“These words are trustworthy and true. And the Lord, the God of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31071Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31071Q\"></sup>the spirits of the prophets, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31071R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31071R\"></sup>has sent his angel to show his servants what must soon take place.”",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“And behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31072S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31072S\"></sup>I am coming soon. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31072T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31072T\"></sup>Blessed is the one who keeps the words of the prophecy of this book.”</span>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>I, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31073U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31073U\"></sup>John, am the one who heard and saw these things. And when I heard and saw them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31073V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31073V\"></sup>I fell down to worship at the feet of the angel who showed them to me,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31074W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31074W\"></sup>but he said to me, “You must not do that! I am a fellow servant with you and your brothers the prophets, and with those <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31074X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31074X\"></sup>who keep the words of this book. Worship God.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And he said to me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31075Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31075Y\"></sup>“Do not seal up the words of the prophecy of this book, for the time is near.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31076Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31076Z\"></sup>Let the evildoer still do evil, and the filthy still be filthy, and the righteous still do right, and the holy still be holy.”",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31077AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31077AA\"></sup>I am coming soon, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31077AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31077AB\"></sup>bringing my recompense with me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31077AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31077AC\"></sup>to repay each one for what he has done.</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31078AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31078AD\"></sup>I am the Alpha and the Omega, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31078AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31078AE\"></sup>the first and the last, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31078AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31078AF\"></sup>the beginning and the end.”</span>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Blessed are those who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31079AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31079AG\"></sup>wash their robes, so that they may have the right to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31079AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31079AH\"></sup>the tree of life and that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31079AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31079AI\"></sup>they may enter the city by the gates.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31080AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31080AJ\"></sup>Outside are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31080AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31080AK\"></sup>the dogs <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31080AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31080AL\"></sup>and sorcerers and the sexually immoral and murderers and idolaters, and everyone who loves and practices falsehood.",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31081AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31081AM\"></sup>“I, Jesus, have sent my angel to testify to you about these things <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31081AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31081AN\"></sup>for the churches. I am <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31081AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31081AO\"></sup>the root and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31081AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31081AP\"></sup>the descendant of David, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31081AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31081AQ\"></sup>the bright morning star.”</span>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>The Spirit and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31082AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31082AR\"></sup>the Bride say, “Come.” And let the one who hears say, “Come.” And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31082AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31082AS\"></sup>let the one who is thirsty come; let the one who desires take the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31082AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31082AT\"></sup>water of life without price.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>I warn everyone who hears the words of the prophecy of this book: <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31083AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31083AU\"></sup>if anyone adds to them, God will add to him the plagues described in this book,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>and if anyone takes away from the words of the book of this prophecy, God will take away his share in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31084AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31084AV\"></sup>the tree of life and in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31084AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31084AW\"></sup>the holy city, which are described in this book.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>He who testifies to these things says, <span class=\"woj\">“Surely <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31085AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31085AX\"></sup>I am coming soon.”</span> Amen. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-31085AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-31085AY\"></sup>Come, Lord Jesus!",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>The grace of the Lord Jesus be with all. Amen."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;